title: Juno

description.plain: Desiring to become pregnant simply due to the way her partner makes her feel, “Juno” cheekily references the 2007 film of the same name, with the protagonist, played by Elliot Page also being pregnant. She ultimately dreams of ending up like the Juno inside the movie, pregnant by someone who truly cares about her and her future concept of having a family.
